Jeffrey 
                                                  L. Hastings, LUTCF
President and CEO 

                                                  Action oriented and a visionary, 
                                                  Jeff Hastings practices what 
                                                  he preaches. As a competitive 
                                                  person, Jeff strives to win 
                                                  at everything he does and has 
                                                  created one of the most successful 
                                                  insurance sales teams across 
                                                  the country.
 
                                                  As President and C.E.O., he 
                                                  has expanded his corporation 
                                                  to include ESProfile.com which 
                                                  is a much needed insurance agent 
                                                  evaluation tool to help business 
                                                  owners select only the most 
                                                  qualified candidates. In addition, 
                                                  he has authored two books and 
                                                  is currently working on his 
                                                  third titled, So You Want 
                                                  to be a Sales Manager which 
                                                  will be available later this 
                                                  year.
 
                                                  Jeff serves on the Farmers Insurance 
                                                  Texas Advisory Board, has been 
                                                  a member of Presidents Council 
                                                  5 years and was selected as 
                                                  the Farmers Insurance District 
                                                  Manager of the Year in 2005. 
                                                  Jeff is a native of Houston, 
                                                  Texas and a graduate of Park 
                                                  University.

                                                  To contact Jeff: 
                                                  


 



