Jeff Hastings
 Director of Product Development
 TeleHealth Services
 Jeff Hastings has over 17 years of experience with healthcare information technology. He has been involved with application development, system design and architecture, project management, product development, product installation, support, strategic planning. He has developed and designed clinical and financial healthcare applications. Additionally, he has managed and implemented multiple applications in the healthcare environment
 With over 5 years as the senior IT executive in multiple hospitals, Mr. Hastings is currently responsible for the design and development of the TigrVue and TigrNet products. Mr Hastings holds a Bachelor of Science in Business Administration from Appalachian State University.


